(49, 1, '2021-04-18 10:22:08', '2021-04-18 10:22:08', 'If you are looking for a sleek and smart-looking gaming laptop, you should consider the Lenovo Ideapad 3 gaming laptop. Allowing you to be a pro at gaming as well as at work, the Ideapad 3 is powered by an AMD Ryzen 5 4600H processor and 8 GB DDR4 3200MHz RAM. The laptop also has Nvidia GeForce GTX 1650 4 GB GDDR6 graphics card so that you can enjoy an exceptional gaming experience. To top it off, you will get a one-month subscription to the Xbox Game Pass on the purchase of this laptop, so you can access over 100 high-quality PC games on Windows 10 devices.\r\n<div class=\"_3qWObK\"><strong>Your Gaming Partner</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"_3zQntF\">\r\n\r\nThe Lenovo Ideapad 3 is an impressive gaming machine that would help you level-up your gameplay. Tipping the scales at 2.2 kg, this well-balanced laptop with a slim profile of 24.9 mm is all set to enhance your gaming experience.\r\n<div class=\"_3qWObK\"><strong>Geared to Perform</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"_3zQntF\">\r\n\r\nPowered by an AMD Ryzen 5 4600H processor and 8 GB DDR4 3200MHz RAM, the Ideapad 3 allows you to seamlessly switch between gaming and work effortlessly. The laptop also features a highly reliable hybrid storage system of 1 TB HDD + 256 SDD that is more than enough to carry your favourite gaming titles, movies, photographs, and more with you.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Lenovo Ideapad Hexa Core 4600H', '<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"_21Ahn-\">NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1650</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"_21Ahn-\">15.6 inch Full HD LED Backlit Anti-glare IPS Display (250 nits Brightness, 60 Hz Refresh Rate)</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"_21Ahn-\">Light Laptop without Optical Disk Drive</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"_21Ahn-\">Pre-installed Genuine Windows 10 OS</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"_1Ma4bX\">No cost EMI starting from ₹9,999/month</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"_1Ma4bX\">Cash on Delivery</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"_1Ma4bX\">Net banking &amp; Credit/ Debit/ ATM card</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish