(326, 1, '2021-04-20 06:05:31', '2021-04-20 06:05:31', 'Amidst your active lifestyle and daily debacles, keep your smartphones and other devices charged by getting the Mi MDY-09-EJ mobile charger. Thanks to its unique technology and design, it supports up to 2 A of fast charging and its micro-USB cable offers up to 480 Mbps of transfer rate for speedy data transfers. Moreover, this compact charger also supports a universal voltage range of approximately 100 V - 240 V, which widens its compatible horizon.\r\n<div class=\"_3qWObK\"><strong>Robust Build and Elegant Design</strong></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"_3zQntF\">\r\n\r\nThe Mi MDY-09-EJ mobile charger is crafted from high-quality materials for prolonged usage. Both the charger and micro-USB cable can withstand heavy-duty use, offering efficient performance.\r\n<div class=\"_3qWObK\"><strong>Feature-rich Charger</strong></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"_3zQntF\">\r\n\r\nWith support for up to 2 A fast charging, this charger lets you quickly charge your compatible devices, thereby saving your precious time. Additionally, it comes with a micro-USB cable that has a length of up to 1.2 meters for rapid data transfer. This cable can offer a data transfer rate of approximately 480 Mbps.\r\n<h3><strong>Specifications</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"_3k-BhJ\">\r\n<h3 class=\"flxcaE\"><strong>General</strong></h3>\r\n<table class=\"_14cfVK\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"_1s_Smc row\">\r\n<td class=\"_1hKmbr col col-3-12\">Sales Package</td>\r\n<td class=\"URwL2w col col-9-12\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"_21lJbe\">1 Charger, USB Cable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"_1s_Smc row\">\r\n<td class=\"_1hKmbr col col-3-12\">Model Number</td>\r\n<td class=\"URwL2w col col-9-12\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"_21lJbe\">MDY-09-EJ</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"_1s_Smc row\">\r\n<td class=\"_1hKmbr col col-3-12\">Output Interface</td>\r\n<td class=\"URwL2w col col-9-12\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"_